719
01:11:29,378 --> 01:11:31,676
Excuse me! Coming through,
coming through!

720
01:11:36,419 --> 01:11:39,582
And now, the ``bond`` cake!

721
01:11:39,789 --> 01:11:41,279
You fixed it!

722
