l tried, you tried!
We were all nice to them.

723
01:11:46,295 --> 01:11:49,093
And they looked at us
like we`re from the zoo.

724
01:11:49,298 --> 01:11:54,531
-Costa, please.
-This ``no`` work. This ``no`` work.

725
01:11:54,737 --> 01:11:58,901
They`re different people. So dry!

726
